article_title: Second open enrollment under the Affordable Care Act going much better than first
article_text:
Second open enrollment under the Affordable Care Act going much better than first

Matthew Hadzick, manager of Highmark Direct store in Allentown, says the second open enrollment under the Affordable Care Act is going much better than the first, largely because of improvements to the online marketplace.
